797
00:44:51,394 --> 00:44:53,163
Kau tak nampak gembira jumpa aku.
Kenapa?

798
00:44:53,296 --> 00:44:54,754
Aku kata,
kau sudah habis bayar.

799
00:44:54,754 --> 00:44:55,988
Tapi kau ingat kerja kita
sudah selesai?

800
00:44:55,988 --> 00:44:57,534
