Kenapa telefon saya?

950
00:52:51,241 --> 00:52:53,176
<i>Saya cuma nak dengar
suara awak.</i>

951
00:52:53,310 --> 00:52:55,245
Boleh saya jumpa awak nanti?

952
00:52:55,378 --> 00:52:57,414
<i>Saya kena memandu lagi.</i>

953
00:52:57,547 --> 00:53:00,983
