00:53:21,170 --> 00:53:22,339
Awak serius?

961
00:53:22,472 --> 00:53:23,840
<i>Ya, Debora.</i>

962
00:53:25,308 --> 00:53:27,244
Awak nak ikut?

963
00:53:27,377 --> 00:53:28,678
Saya nak, Baby.

964
00:53:29,512 --> 00:53:30,680
<i>Jumpa lagi.</i>

965
00:53:40,957 --> 00:53:42,525


966
00:53:42,659 --> 00:53:44,503


967
00:53:44,527 --> 00:53:45,562


968
00:53:45,695 --> 00:53:46,695


969
00:53:46,763 --> 00:53:48,164


970
00:53:49,098 --> 00:53:50,166
Itu dia.

971
00:53:51,801 --> 00:53:53,035
Hei, Baby!

972
00:53:53,169 --> 00:53:54,971
Si Pekak datang balik?

973
00:53:55,104 --> 00:53:57,307
Kau pernah nampak kerja budak ini?
- Ya, pernah.

974
00:53:57,440 --> 00:53:59,175
Rasanya Doc suka dia...

975
00:53:59,309 --> 00:54:01,086
...sebab dia boleh letak kereta
di tempat orang cacat di depan bank.

976
00:54:01,110 --> 00:54:03,179
Tempat orang cacat?
- Ya.

977
00:54:03,313 --> 00:54:05,524
Dia ada masalah dengan pendengaran,
Tinnitus atau seangkatannya.

978
00:54:05,548 --> 00:54:08,184
Lagi pun, dia perlu dengar muzik
24 jam sehari...

979
00:54:08,318 --> 00:54:09,986
...untuk tenggelamkan bunyi
di dalam telinganya.

980
00:54:10,119 --> 00:54:11,488
Alamak!

981
00:54:11,621 --> 00:54:16,058
Kau tahu siapa yang
ada masalah yang sama?

982
00:54:16,192 --> 00:54:17,427
Barbra Streisand.

983
00:54:17,560 --> 00:54:20,586
Kau rasa, kau nampak
aku jenis yang kenal Barbra Streisand?

984
00:54:20,586 --> 00:54:23,915
Hei, jaga mulut kau.
